overview.en:
The biggest meaning of the coin god ICO188 is that it can closely link 
    investors and project parties,through the rapid collection of market big data and 
    supplemented by mature familiar analysis team,more comprehensive,more objective and 
    more realistic project consultation and the evaluation report makes it easier for   
    every investor to find a more professional,higher quality and more suitable ICO 
    project,and also enjoy the one-stop service provided by the platform.
overview.zh:
币财神ICO188的最大意义源自于它能够将投资者与项目方紧密地联系在一起，通过市场
    大数据快速采集再辅以成熟的熟悉分析团队，更全面、更客观、更真实的项目咨询和评估报告，让每一个
    投资者可以更轻松地在这里找寻到更专业、更高质、更适合自己的ICO项目，同时还可以享受到平台所提
    供的一站式服务。
